SUMMARY:Summer Fete
DESCRIPTION:Our annual Summer Fete on the Hut grounds — bouncy castle\, BBQ\, raffle\, plus a chance for parents to meet the leadership team and learn about the year ahead.\nVolunteers welcome — get in touch if you can help with the BBQ or the gates rota.\n
LOCATION:Anytown Scout Hut
URL:http://localhost:1313/events/2026-07-12-summer-fete/
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2026-08-14-cubs-summer-camp@localhost:1313
DTSTAMP:20260513T184246Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260814
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260817
SUMMARY:Cubs Summer Camp
DESCRIPTION:Three days under canvas at Pioneer Camp — Friday afternoon arrival\, Sunday afternoon collection. The Pack will be running a mix of campcraft\, water activities and the all-time-favourite night hike.\nKit list and consent forms will be sent home four weeks ahead of camp. Bursary support is available — speak to Akela in confidence if cost would otherwise stop your Cub joining us.\n
LOCATION:Pioneer Camp\, Buckinghamshire
URL:http://localhost:1313/events/2026-08-14-cubs-summer-camp/
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
