DTSTART;TZID=Europe/London:20260926T193000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/London:20260926T210000
SUMMARY:Leaders' Safeguarding Refresher
DESCRIPTION:A short refresher on safeguarding policy and the YP-protection module for all leaders\, helpers and exec members. Plenty of time for questions and a cuppa.\nMandatory if your check is up for renewal in the next six months.\n
LOCATION:Anytown Scout Hut
URL:http://localhost:1313/events/2026-09-26-leaders-training/
STATUS:CANCELLED
